subject: Basketball (College)
NCAA Basketball Championships (Men)
lead_paragraph: Gonzaga, which had secured the first No. 1 seed in university history, fell to No. 9 Wichita State, exiting the N.C.A.A. tournament before the second week for the fourth straight year.
